# Supabase Community Project (auth, members, posts, teams, etc.)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-community-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-community-anon-key

# Note: The CMS Supabase project (welfare projects, blogs) is configured
# directly in src/lib/supabase.ts — it uses the public anon key and
# does not require environment variables since it's read-only public data.
